# Description

Proxy allowing to compute single value from a submodel. E.g. when top-level model contains rows representing tokens by token symbol and has role holding submodel storing balances per chain, it's useful to have a sum of all per-chain balances as a top-level role. This proxy is intended to provide possibility of adding such roles based on submodels in an effective and dynamic way.

Possible API/example of usage:

```
ListModel {
    id: srcModel
    
    ListElement {
        tookenName: "ETH"

        balances: [
            ListElement { chainId: "1", balance: 3 },
            ListElement { chainId: "2",  balance: 4 },
            ListElement { chainId: "31", balance: 2 }
        ]
    }
    
    ListElement {
        tookenName: "SNT"
        color2: "red2"

        balances: [
            ListElement { chainId: "2", balance: 42 }
        ]
    }
    
    ListElement {
        tookenName: "DAI"

        balances: [
            ListElement { chainId: "1",  balance: 4 },
            ListElement { chainId: "3", balance: 9 }
        ]
    }
}


AggregationModel {
    sourceModel: srcModel

    aggregations: [
        Aggregation {
            submodelRole: "balances"
            aggregateRoleName: "totalBalance"
    
            initialValue: 0
    
            submodelAggregationRule: function(accumulator, model) {
                return accumulator + model.balance 
            }
        }
    ]
}
```

Expected output model:
```
ListModel {
    ListElement {
        tookenName: "ETH"

        totalBalance: 9
        balances: [
            ListElement { chainId: "1", balance: 3 },
            ListElement { chainId: "2",  balance: 4 },
            ListElement { chainId: "31", balance: 2 }
        ]
    }
    
    ListElement {
        tookenName: "SNT"
        color2: "red2"

        totalBalance: 42
        balances: [
            ListElement { chainId: "2", balance: 42 }
        ]
    }
    
    ListElement {
        tookenName: "DAI"

        totalBalance: 13
        balances: [
            ListElement { chainId: "1",  balance: 4 },
            ListElement { chainId: "3", balance: 9 }
        ]
    }
}
```
